                <note rend="inline" type="source">500.A15A4/898: Telegram</note>
                <head>
                    <hi rend="italic">The <gloss type="from">Secretary of State</gloss> to the
                        Acting Chairman of the American Delegation (<persName corresp="#p_GHS1"
                            type="to">Gibson</persName>)</hi>
                </head>
                <opener>
                    <dateline rendition="#right">
                        <placeName>
                            <hi rend="smallcaps">Washington</hi>
                        </placeName>, <date calendar="gregorian" when="1932-03-03T16:00:00-05:00"
                            >March 3, 1932—4 p.m.</date>
                    </dateline>
                </opener>
                <p>27. Your 54, March 2, 9 p.m. The Department concurs in your conclusions as to
                    method of procedure.</p>
                <closer>
                    <signed>
                        <persName corresp="#p_SHL1">
                            <hi rend="smallcaps">Stimson</hi>
                        </persName>
                    </signed>
                </closer>
            </div>
        </body>
